      <div class="chi-siamo-text reveal">
        <h2>How Build Hub was born</h2>
        <p>Build Hub is rooted in direct experience gained on construction sites, in site supervision and in the coordination of technical and operational teams. Over the years we have observed a recurring issue: far too many projects stall not through lack of skill, but through the absence of a guiding figure capable of holding all the pieces together. Professionals, contractors and suppliers often operate in a disconnected way, generating delays, misunderstandings and unexpected costs. It is from this realisation that Build Hub was created: an idea born to bring order to complexity, offering a structured approach to managing construction projects with coordination, planning and oversight at its core. Today we assist private clients, professionals and companies as a single interlocutor, building a bridge between the various parties involved and ensuring a clear, shared and measurable vision of the goals to be achieved.</p>
        <p>We are convinced that every project — regardless of its size or complexity — deserves structured, transparent and results-oriented management. For this reason our involvement does not end with design or the purely technical aspects, but embraces the entire lifecycle of the work: from the preliminary phase through to project handover.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

